Title: Emily: A Visualization Tool for Large Sparse Matrices  
Author: T. Loos and R. Bramley 
Abstract: A visualization tool for large sparse matrices and its usage is described. Examples are given, including viewing the effect of preconditioning for iterative methods for linear systems and using the tool to provide a more informative view of domain partitioning for parallel processing. Keywords sparse matrices, visualization, iterative methods, domain decomposition 
